N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4830.4 - Licensee to be informed of revocation proceedings

State Regulations

Proceedings to revoke a license shall be brought by
informing the licensee in writing of the grounds thereof and the date and place
set for hearing thereon. Notes
